notifications.body:
05/01/2017

Dear supplier, 

Ben's Awesome Company’s application to Digital Outcomes and Specialists 2 was successful.

Your results were: 
• Digital outcomes - yes
no
maybe
I don't know

We’ve notified all applicants about their results. A 10-day 'standstill period' will start on 17 January 2017 and end at 11.59pm (GMT) on 26 January 2017. We expect the framework to be awarded on 27 January 2017 and services to go live on the Digital Marketplace in February 2016. 

You must sign and return your framework agreement before you can sell services on the Digital Marketplace. 

Your framework agreement is ready to sign at: 
https://www.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/suppliers/frameworks/digital-outcomes-and-specialists-2/agreement


We’ll notify you when the standstill period is over. Until then, you shouldn’t make any public announcements about the result of your application.

Yours faithfully,
Alison Lisett
Head of Sourcing Delivery
Crown Commercial Service
notifications.subject: Your Digital Outcomes and Specialists 2 application has been successful
